<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
No, that's the only way.  <P>To make it take effect faster, always fight with a haste-type spell on you -- quickness or alacrity or enchanter's haste.  The more hits, the faster it goes up.<P>There is another alternative though, that is a way of raising weapons skills without doing it in the field -- go buy the skill raises at the trainer with your points and some extra cash.  It's fairly cheap at lower levels, and pretty expensive at higher ones, and always costs points.
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
