Level 16?  No, that's not much of a problem at all.   I don't think I have time to keep all 3 of my weapon skills maxed.  Hrm, I suppose I could max out my 1hb but that would take a couple days work of no exp fighting  <IMG SRC="tongue.gif" border="0"><P>I would go to the trainer in Halas (if you're close by) and train up 2hb to 20 (that's where it's still free, right?) and then go slugging with the 2hb.   Keep your dex maxed as high as possible, dex helps with learning weapon skills.<P>At the very minimum, pick 2 of them and keep them maxed, keep the third high just in case you find yourself wanting it.  At lvl 36 my 2hb is 146 (2 short of max), pierce is 147 (1 short) and 1hb is about 110.<P>Seriously, you're not too high for it to be a problem.  When I started lvl 35 my 1 and 2hb were both in the low 100s.  I raised my 2hb by soloing mountain giants in FM.<P>- Taladaen 36th level Shaman<BR>Brell Serilis
