<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
You're fine at 16, it's not too late.<P>I'd max piercing because it's most important, and besides that concentrate on 2h blunt because those weapons are naturally slow, and fewer swings will level you more slowly.<P>There are a couple of one hand blunts out there, but if you do piercing you will have one-hand and shield covered, so instead of developing it twice with different weapons, I'd go for the 2h blunt as a supplement.  <P>You might want to invest in very quick weapons, even if they don't do much damage.  For instance, a ketchatka koro mis 2h blunt is 7/30, which is very very fast for a 2h blunt, and usually costs 50 plat or well under.  A beetlestinger, in my server's destroyed economy, is getting cheaper all the time, and is 8/23, for a spear.  Probably well out of your price range now, at about 1000 plat (my server), but something really quick is what you want when you're raising weapons skills.
</FONT>
