Heya guys. Just wanted to try to help you out here. Skills need raising? What raises them? Think hard now. That's right! Skills are raised when fighting NPC's within our range. So what does all this mean? Find a nice magician or necro to summon a pet your level. Buff yourself up. Then duel them. When you or the pet is about to die, just backoff (him too) and regen back to full. This is a great, fun, and safe way to raise skills. <P>Lornuk Mojorisen<BR>47th Shaman of Quellious
</FONT>
